arStrings.szText: We donated our dead to the necromancers studying in Necropolis. Only this time, they didn’t lift the dead -- they enraged their spirits.
Rumor has it that an apprentice tried to enhance their abilities by extracting essence from the corpses.
The dead felt betrayed and went wild, consuming the apprentice and several necromancers’ spirits.
We tried to recover our dead. Let them find rest, but their anger and hatred were impossible to soothe. We can only pray that one day, they will find peace.
